Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_tx::_pause_zero

AGL_GMX_TX_PAUSE_ZERO = Packet TX Amount of time remaining to backpressure

Notes: Additionally reset when MIX<prt>_CTL[RESET] is set to 1.
